metadata.description:
camoufly & msft represent the newest generation of bedroom producers who have taken DIY to a completely new level. camoufly's casually professional production style combines a bright modern style with nostalgic synthesizer leads, while msft has managed to craft a darker edge to his sound. This can be heard in this cycle's curated sample, with sounds recorded in Milan, Italy using a Korg Opsix, a Tasty Chips GR-1 and a DSI Prophet 08.

    This hedsTAPE was curated by camoufly & msft during a collaborative production cycle. Each track is accompanied by a visualizer, and the entire mix is included with each mint. The talented artists featured in this mix have been chosen anonymously via heds community curation, and appear in the following order:
    
    George Hooks
    Green Ring 
    Pala Chrome
    Filoo 
    fugue 
    billings 
    Fresh Stuff 
    rage logic 
    Robu 
    Max Fry
    
    Find out how to participate @ heds.app
metadata.name: hedsTAPE 12 #1
